data.description: Welcome to North Fort Myers, where your paradise awaits! This charming home offers an incredible opportunity to live in a highly desirable area with low tax rates, excellent schools, and easy access to I-75 and US 41. You'll love the convenience of having shopping, dining, and the beautiful downtown Fort Myers just minutes away. Talk about upgrades, This home offers new hurricane impact windows and doors to ensure security and peace of mind. The kitchen has been tastefully upgraded with new cabinets, quartz counter tops, a mobile island for extra counter space and modern appliances. The entire home features new AC ducts and returns in every room for efficient cooling. This home has been recently RE-PIPED! Fresh soffit, fascia and gutters enhance both the appearance and maintenance of the property. A new well water system provides a reliable and convenient water source. The electrical system has been updated with can lights installed throughout the home. This home presents an exceptional opportunity to settle into a comfortable and modern space in North Fort Myers. Schedule a showing today and experience the potential of this fantastic property!
